│ +  // ensure that the instructions are not used by any other │
│ instruction that is                                          │
│ +  // not being deleted. This can happen in cases where the  │
│ vectorizer runs                                              │
│ +  // multiple horizontal reduction passes on the same       │
│ block. We must be careful                                    │
│ +  // not to replace uses in debug intrinsics.               │
│ +  for (Instruction *I : RemovedInsts)                       │
